response.overview: SHINE Wrestling presents  SHINE 11,  Ybor City, FL,  7.12.13.  Matches include:  Event Hostess – Chasity Taylor.  SHINE Championship Tournament  • Bracket A Fatal Four Way Qualifier – Winner Faces Rain in the First Round  Mercedes Martinez vs. Nikki Roxx vs. LuFisto vs. Su Yung  • Bracket B Fatal Four Way Qualifier – Winner Faces Santana in the First Round  Amazing Kong vs. Angelina Love vs. Ivelisse vs. Kimberly  • Bracket A First Round Match -- Sweet Saraya Knight vs. Jessicka Havok  • Bracket A First Round Match -- Rain w/ April Hunter vs. Bracket A Fatal Four Way Winner  • Bracket B First Round Match -- Leva vs. Mia Yim  • Bracket B First Round Match -- Santana vs. Bracket B Fatal Four Way Winner.  Plus – Semi-Finals & Finals, as well as “The Scream Queen” Daffney
